column5: Out to Camp Jiggy Jiggy.. Holy crap is it quiet out here.. been 6 months since were last here.  Everything in perfect condition for another year thankfully.  Ha da bit of Crown to power down last night and slept for 10 hours.. best sleepy poo I can remember lol.. sure is quiet out here....  anyway went for a quick troll up the river and Monique managed this one!
Have fun you too. Work hard and play hard. Watch that Crown it messes with your head.😁
I have  ‘64 Crown. may never open it!
I was born in 64.....   bring it it my wake.. lol
Damn, you are just a baby!
